An earlier version of the dataset required users to perform the join in ArcGIS between published shape files and data files. This version includes shape files with the data already joined. For those administrative regions with missing data, this is indicated with a value of -99999. The user must exclude these values before visualizing or analyzing the data.</dct:description>         <dcat:keyword>WWHGD</dcat:keyword>         <dcat:keyword>geospatial</dcat:keyword>
